nodes.body: Please move the file to `Algebra/` instead, since I think mixing multiplication and zero places it outside group theory topicwise.

Now that I look at this again, the definition of `nonZeroDivisors` is definitionally equal to `nonZeroDivisorsLeft`. Should we make the former an `abbrev` of the latter? (Or maybe the other way around)
